 MDC spin density (spinA - spinB)
 -------------------------------- 
 Reported here are the the number of Alpha-electrons minus the number of Beta-electrons
 per atom, which usually are regarded as spin densities.

        Atom    Level:     MDC-m        MDC-d        MDC-q
 ---------------------------------------------------------
     1     B            1.000000     1.000000     1.000000

